net.bytebuddy.implementation

Class FieldAccessor.ForImplicitProperty

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.bytebuddy.implementation.FieldAccessor
      • net.bytebuddy.implementation.FieldAccessor.ForImplicitProperty
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InstrumentedType.Prepareable, FieldAccessor.AssignerConfigurable, FieldAccessor.OwnerTypeLocatable, FieldAccessor.PropertyConfigurable, Implementation
    Enclosing class:
    FieldAccessor

    protected static class FieldAccessor.ForImplicitProperty
extends FieldAccessor
implements FieldAccessor.OwnerTypeLocatable
    A field accessor for an implicit property where a getter or setter property is inferred from the signature.
